01:20:37.063 --> 01:20:38.438
Hello.
Dewey.

1260
01:20:38.604 --> 01:20:40.688
Sidney. where are you?!
I'm at Kirby's.

1261
01:20:40.854 --> 01:20:42.354
The Killer is here. I need your help.

1262
01:20:42.521 --> 01:20:44.354
I'm on my way.

1263
01:20:44.521 --> 01:20:46.688
Oh!

1264
01:20:46.854 --> 01:20:48.854
Sidney? Sidney?!

1265
01:20:49.021 --> 01:20:51.521
I need all units
to 329 Whispering Lane.

1266
01:20:51.688 --> 01:20:54.271
All units. 329 Whispering Lane!

1267
01:21:14.479 --> 01:21:17.854
Sorry. It's just me. Look. I tried to
call 911 but the landline's dead.

1268
01:21:18.021 --> 01:21:20.438
Someone smashed the router.
I think I got through on my cell.

1269
01:21:20.604 --> 01:21:22.563
OK. where's Jill?

1270
01:21:22.729 --> 01:21:25.979
Oh. God. Get in. Go. go. go.

1271
01:21:28.854 --> 01:21:31.563
There's a room down here.
We can lock ourselves in.

1272
01:21:31.729 --> 01:21:33.854
I heard you yelling to Jill.
Did she get away?

1273
01:21:34.021 --> 01:21:35.854
I think she's safe.

1274
01:21:43.188 --> 01:21:46.688
Kirby. let me in!
Charlie.

1275
01:21:48.229 --> 01:21:51.729
No. no. no. I just found Robbie.
This is his blood.

1276
01:21:51.896 --> 01:21:55.354
Please. please. There is
someone else out here. Let me in.

1277
01:21:55.521 --> 01:21:57.688
If you can't trust him.
don't open the door.

1278
01:21:58.938 --> 01:22:00.604
Oh. my God. let me in!

1279
01:22:00.771 --> 01:22:02.146
Get away from the door. Charlie.

1280
01:22:02.313 --> 01:22:04.271
Kirby. it is me. Please let me in!

1281
01:22:04.438 --> 01:22:06.396
Get away from the door. Charlie!

1282
01:22:06.563 --> 01:22:07.771
It's me!

1283
01:22:09.604 --> 01:22:11.646
I'm sorry. I can't.

1284
01:22:11.813 --> 01:22:13.313
What the fuck?

1285
01:22:13.479 --> 01:22:15.021
I'm sorry.

1286
01:22:15.188 --> 01:22:16.938
Behind you! Look out!

1287
01:22:17.104 --> 01:22:18.396
Ohh!

1288
01:22:19.438 --> 01:22:22.729
Ohh! No. no. no. no. Please.

1289
01:22:22.896 --> 01:22:25.104
Kirby!

1290
01:22:35.229 --> 01:22:37.688
Oh. no. God. no. please.

1291
01:22:37.854 --> 01:22:39.479
Leave him alone!

1292
01:22:39.646 --> 01:22:41.313
Leave him alone!

1293
01:22:43.521 --> 01:22:46.563
It's Charlie's phone.

1294
01:22:47.604 --> 01:22:50.438
Tell Sidney
heads are gonna roll tonight.

1295
01:22:50.604 --> 01:22:52.563
Tell Sidney it's all because of her.

1296
01:22:52.729 --> 01:22:54.771
Or maybe she wants
to take his place?

1297
01:22:54.938 --> 01:22:56.604
I promise to be quick.

1298
01:22:56.771 --> 01:22:58.479
It's him.
OK. OK.

1299
01:22:58.646 --> 01:23:00.896
I"m gonna get Jill.
We should be in the same place.

1300
01:23:01.063 --> 01:23:03.688
Just keep him on the phone.
I'll be right back. OK?

1301
01:23:05.521 --> 01:23:06.979
Let him go. please.

1302
01:23:07.146 --> 01:23:09.438
I hear you like
horror movies. Kirby.

1303
01:23:09.604 --> 01:23:12.063
but do you like them as much as him?

1304
01:23:12.229 --> 01:23:15.604
Forget watching 'Stab'.
You get to live it.

1305
01:23:15.771 --> 01:23:18.771
No. no. no. no. no.
He's the expert. It's not me.

1306
01:23:18.938 --> 01:23:21.104
Warm-up question —
Jason's weapon?

1307
01:23:21.271 --> 01:23:23.354
Uh. it's a machete.

1308
01:23:23.521 --> 01:23:26.604
There. You see?
You do know the genre.

1309
01:23:26.771 --> 01:23:29.646
Michael Myers?
Uh. a butcher knife.

1310
01:23:29.813 --> 01:23:32.521
Leatherface?
A chainsaw. Please!

1311
01:23:32.688 --> 01:23:34.813
Just ask Sidney if you need
some help. Freddy Krueger?

1312
01:23:34.979 --> 01:23:36.396
Uh. razor hands.

1313
01:23:36.563 --> 01:23:38.646
Name the movie that
started the slasher craze...

1314
01:23:38.813 --> 01:23:40.271
'Halloween'.
'Texas Chainsaw Massacre'.

1315
01:23:40.438 --> 01:23:41.854
'Last House on the Left'
or 'Psycho'.

1316
01:23:42.021 --> 01:23:44.521
'Psycho'.
None of the above!

1317
01:23:44.688 --> 01:23:47.021
'Peeping Tom'. 1960.
directed by Michael Powell...

1318
01:23:47.188 --> 01:23:50.146
first movie to ever put
the audience in the killer's POV.

1319
01:23:50.313 --> 01:23:52.688
What? Wait. No. no. no. no.

1320
01:23:52.854 --> 01:23:55.229
Please just ask me
one more question. Just one more.

1321
01:23:55.396 --> 01:23:57.521
Alright. Kirby.

1322
01:23:57.688 --> 01:24:01.271
Then it's time for your
last-chance question.

1323
01:24:01.438 --> 01:24:04.479
Name the remake of the groundbreaking
horror movie

1324
01:24:04.646 --> 01:24:06.104
in which the villain...

1325
01:24:06.271 --> 01:24:08.021
'Halloween'. 'Texas Chainsaw'.

1326
01:24:08.188 --> 01:24:09.896
'Dawn of the Dead".
'The Hills Have Eyes'.

1327
01:24:10.063 --> 01:24:12.604
'Amityville Horror'.
'Last House on the Left'.

1328
01:24:12.771 --> 01:24:15.188
'Friday the 13th'.
'A Nightmare on Elm Street'.

1329
01:24:15.354 --> 01:24:17.813
'My Bloody Valentine'.
'When a Stranger Calls'.

1330
01:24:17.979 --> 01:24:19.854
'Prom Night'. 'Black Christmas'.

1331
01:24:20.021 --> 01:24:21.729
'House of Wax'. 'The Fog'.

1332
01:24:21.896 --> 01:24:23.271
Uh. 'Piranha'.

1333
01:24:23.438 --> 01:24:26.688
It's one of those. right? Right?

1334
01:24:34.063 --> 01:24:37.354
I got it right. I was fucking right.

1335
01:24:37.521 --> 01:24:39.104
Jill?

1336
01:24:50.938 --> 01:24:53.271
I won. Charlie. I fucking won.

1337
01:24:53.438 --> 01:24:56.438
I won. He tried to beat me.
but I fucking won.

1338
01:24:56.604 --> 01:24:58.521
Right. Kirby.

1339
01:24:58.688 --> 01:25:01.563
Hold on. OK.

1340
01:25:01.729 --> 01:25:03.646
Almost there. Just hang tight.

1341
01:25:03.813 --> 01:25:07.229
OK. OK. Alright.
Kirby.

1342
01:25:07.396 --> 01:25:09.021
This is making a move.

1343
01:25:09.188 --> 01:25:10.438
Ohh!

1344
01:25:12.688 --> 01:25:15.313
Four years of classes together.
You notice me now?

1345
01:25:15.479 --> 01:25:17.604
You stupid bitch.

1346
01:25:17.771 --> 01:25:19.979
It's too late.
Ohh!

1347
01:25:20.146 --> 01:25:23.146
Shh. shh. I know. I know.

1348
01:25:23.313 --> 01:25:25.813
It's OK. Take your time.

1349
01:25:25.979 --> 01:25:29.313
It doesn't happen as fast
as it does in the movies. I know.

1350
01:25:29.479 --> 01:25:31.896
Ch...

1351
01:25:32.063 --> 01:25:33.604
Charlie. Charlie.

1352
01:25:33.771 --> 01:25:36.354
Ohh!

1353
01:25:58.104 --> 01:25:59.313
Kirby?

1354
01:25:59.479 --> 01:26:01.563
Oh!

1355
01:26:03.063 --> 01:26:06.104
You know. you learn a lot when
you watch movies over and over.

1356
01:26:06.271 --> 01:26:08.938
All the plots are about
trying to kill you.

1357
01:26:09.979 --> 01:26:11.354
Where's Jill?

1358
01:26:11.521 --> 01:26:14.521
Oh. you think she's gonna get away?
You think anyone gets away?

1359
01:26:14.688 --> 01:26:16.521
Argaht Ohh!

1360
01:26:17.563 --> 01:26:19.104
Ohh!

1361
01:26:24.938 --> 01:26:26.396
Jill.

1362
01:26:26.563 --> 01:26:29.229
Hello. Sidney. Surprised?

1363
01:26:30.271 --> 01:26:31.646
Watch this.

1364
01:26:31.813 --> 01:26:38.021
<i>This is the part. my dear cousin.
when the cameras.. Turn off.</i>

1365
01:26:42.104 --> 01:26:44.396
Charlie...
Already taken care of.

1366
01:26:44.563 --> 01:26:46.771
Man. I got great footage
of my Robbie Kill.

1367
01:26:46.938 --> 01:26:49.438
better than Jenny and Marnie
or Olivia even.

1368
01:26:49.604 --> 01:26:52.521
Good. We'll cut and upload it later
and make it all traceable to Trevor.

1369
01:26:52.688 --> 01:26:54.688
Speaking of which...

1370
01:26:57.979 --> 01:27:00.063
Remind you of anything?
Jill. please.

1371
01:27:00.229 --> 01:27:01.854
Shut up! Dick.

1372
01:27:02.021 --> 01:27:03.479
Everything I learned.
I learned from you.

1373
01:27:03.646 --> 01:27:06.104
You think you had
a shitty boyfriend. Sidney?

1374
01:27:06.271 --> 01:27:11.854
Here's one that fucks you. dumps you
and doesn't even make you famous.

1375
01:27:12.021 --> 01:27:14.896
Arggh! What the fuck. Jill?
I loved you!

1376
01:27:15.063 --> 01:27:17.354
Shut the fuck up already!

1377
01:27:17.521 --> 01:27:19.521
Ohh! Arggh!

1378
01:27:19.688 --> 01:27:23.521
I'm sure those cops want you
to have this. Jill. for your protection.

1379
01:27:23.688 --> 01:27:25.354
Wait...

1380
01:27:26.521 --> 01:27:29.896
Baby. please. Baby. please.

1381
01:27:30.063 --> 01:27:32.313
Shouldn't have killed
all those people. Trev.

1382
01:27:32.479 --> 01:27:34.396
gone and put it on video even.

1383
01:27:34.563 --> 01:27:36.813
but it means a lot
that you did it for me.

1384
01:27:36.979 --> 01:27:39.021
What the fuck are you talking about?

1385
01:27:39.188 --> 01:27:42.771
I am not the girl you cheat on.

1386
01:27:42.938 --> 01:27:44.938
Arggh! Fuck!

1387
01:27:47.354 --> 01:27:49.729
I've gone through everything.
We're definitely good on time line.

1388
01:27:49.896 --> 01:27:52.229
Oh. yeah. we're perfect.

1389
01:27:52.396 --> 01:27:53.938
No. no. no. Please.

1390
01:27:55.104 --> 01:27:56.146
Ohh...

1391
01:27:57.229 --> 01:27:59.146
That should keep him quiet.

1392
01:28:01.563 --> 01:28:03.604
Ready for act three?

1393
01:28:03.771 --> 01:28:05.729
Got it figured out yet. Sidney?

1394
01:28:05.896 --> 01:28:07.688
In keeping with our remake theme.

1395
01:28:07.854 --> 01:28:10.396
Trevor's this generation's
Billy Loomis.

1396
01:28:10.563 --> 01:28:13.729
and we"re the innocent victims —
Sidney and Randy.

1397
01:28:13.896 --> 01:28:17.521
See. with you. the world just
heard about what happened

1398
01:28:17.688 --> 01:28:20.396
but with us. they're gonna see it.

1399
01:28:20.563 --> 01:28:22.229
It's gonna be a worldwide sensation.

1400
01:28:22.396 --> 01:28:24.396
I mean. people have gotta see this shit.

1401
01:28:24.563 --> 01:28:27.729
It's not like anyone reads any more.

1402
01:28:27.896 --> 01:28:34.188
We"re gonna know fame
like you never even dreamed of.

1403
01:28:34.354 --> 01:28:36.229
Last two teenagers standing.

1404
01:28:37.271 --> 01:28:39.479
This time Randy gets the girl.

1405
01:28:44.438 --> 01:28:45.896
You were amazing.

1406
01:28:46.063 --> 01:28:47.563
You're the perfect victim.

1407
01:28:47.729 --> 01:28:51.563
I was so believable today. wasn't I?

1408
01:28:51.729 --> 01:28:55.729
I mean. I told so many lies that
I actually started to believe them.

1409
01:28:55.896 --> 01:28:58.146
I really think that
I was born for this.

1410
01:28:58.313 --> 01:29:00.063
How could you do this?

1411
01:29:01.979 --> 01:29:05.188
Do you know what it was like
growing up in this family.

1412
01:29:05.354 --> 01:29:07.563
related to you?

1413
01:29:07.729 --> 01:29:11.146
I mean. all I ever heard was
“Sidney this” and “Sidney that”

1414
01:29:11.313 --> 01:29:13.521
and “Sidney. Sidney. Sidney”.

1415
01:29:13.688 --> 01:29:16.688
You were always just
so fucking special!

1416
01:29:16.854 --> 01:29:19.146
Well. now I'm the special one.

1417
01:29:19.313 --> 01:29:22.229
You'll slip. They always do.

1418
01:29:22.396 --> 01:29:24.563
Come on. Charlie.
let's get on with this.

1419
01:29:27.021 --> 01:29:31.271
You have to be strong
and hold still. OK?

1420
01:29:31.438 --> 01:29:34.729
Yeah. Yeah. old-school.
like Billy and Stu.

1421
01:29:34.896 --> 01:29:36.938
Come on. baby. get it up.

1422
01:29:37.104 --> 01:29:38.479
Come on.

1423
01:29:38.646 --> 01:29:41.479
Shoulder me. shoulder me.
shoulder me. Get it up!

1424
01:29:45.646 --> 01:29:49.438
The heart?
That's not the way we rehearsed it.

1425
01:29:49.604 --> 01:29:53.146
You said it. Charlie —
Billy and Stu. Trevor and you.

1426
01:29:53.313 --> 01:29:56.604
What the media really loves. baby.

1427
01:29:56.771 --> 01:29:58.646
IS a sole survivor.

1428
01:29:58.813 --> 01:30:01.021
Just ask you know who.

1429
01:30:01.188 --> 01:30:05.938
Trevor was your partner.
You — you were the idea man.

1430
01:30:15.938 --> 01:30:17.688
Even your friends?

1431
01:30:18.729 --> 01:30:20.438
My friends?

1432
01:30:20.604 --> 01:30:24.188
What world are you living in?
I don't need friends.

1433
01:30:24.354 --> 01:30:26.521
I need fans.

1434
01:30:26.688 --> 01:30:28.063
Don't you get it?!

1435
01:30:28.229 --> 01:30:31.771
This has never been
about killing you.

1436
01:30:31.938 --> 01:30:34.896
It's about becoming you.

1437
01:30:35.063 --> 01:30:37.604
I mean. for fuck's sake.
my own mother had to die...

1438
01:30:37.771 --> 01:30:41.104
no great loss there —
so I could stay true to the original.

1439
01:30:41.271 --> 01:30:43.021
That's sick. right?

1440
01:30:43.188 --> 01:30:47.021
Well. sick is the new sane.

1441
01:30:47.188 --> 01:30:50.604
You had your 15 minutes.
now I want mine!

1442
01:30:50.771 --> 01:30:52.313
I mean. what am I supposed to do?

1443
01:30:52.479 --> 01:30:56.771
Go to college. grad school. work?

1444
01:30:56.938 --> 01:31:00.604
Look around — we all live in public now.
we're all on the internet.

1445
01:31:00.771 --> 01:31:03.479
How do you think people
become famous any more?!

1446
01:31:03.646 --> 01:31:07.104
You don't have to achieve anything.

1447
01:31:07.271 --> 01:31:11.146
You just gotta have
fucked-up shit happen to you.

1448
01:31:11.313 --> 01:31:14.188
So. you do have to die. Sid.

1449
01:31:14.354 --> 01:31:18.313
Those are the rules —
new movie. new franchise.

1450
01:31:18.479 --> 01:31:20.354
There's only room for one lead

1451
01:31:20.521 --> 01:31:24.021
and let's face it.
your ingenue days. they're over.

1452
01:31:30.104 --> 01:31:32.563
Don't tell me you didn't know
this day would come.

1453
01:32:51.604 --> 01:32:54.896
Oh. fuck!

1454
01:34:14.896 --> 01:34:16.938
Come on. let's move it!

1455
01:34:24.313 --> 01:34:25.771
He's gone.

1456
01:34:25.938 --> 01:34:29.021
Check the rooms both sides
and upstairs.

1457
01:34:29.188 --> 01:34:30.729
Yes. ma'am.

1458
01:34:47.438 --> 01:34:49.604
Jill. can you give us
a description of the murderer?

1459
01:34:49.771 --> 01:34:51.354
Jill. over here.
Jill. what happened in there?

1460
01:35:03.479 --> 01:35:05.938
Jill. how does it feel to be a hero?

1461
01:35:12.771 --> 01:35:16.021
It's OK. You're gonna be OK.

1462
01:35:17.188 --> 01:35:21.604
Jill. you made it.
That's all that matters.

1463
01:35:21.771 --> 01:35:24.063
Trevor and Charlie.
they tried to kill me.

1464
01:35:24.229 --> 01:35:27.021
And I heard they killed
my mom and...

1465
01:35:27.188 --> 01:35:28.979
...and Robbie and Kirby too.

1466
01:35:29.146 --> 01:35:30.354
Shh.

1467
01:35:30.521 --> 01:35:33.021
Just lay back.
try to rest.

1468
01:35:34.729 --> 01:35:36.479
Is... is your wife...?

1469
01:35:37.979 --> 01:35:40.896
She's gonna be fine.
She's recovering.

1470
01:35:42.313 --> 01:35:46.313
If I ever write a book one day.
I'd want her to write it with me.

1471
01:35:46.479 --> 01:35:51.146
We'd be a good team with
our matching wounds and all.

1472
01:35:53.771 --> 01:35:55.521
We're survivors now.

1473
01:35:56.938 --> 01:35:59.313
I just wish Sidney was too.

1474
01:35:59.479 --> 01:36:05.271
Jill... they're not sure yet.
It's still touch and go.

1475
01:36:05.438 --> 01:36:07.938
But she's in ICU.

1476
01:36:08.104 --> 01:36:11.104
And they think
Sidney just might make it.

1477
01:36:12.396 --> 01:36:13.771
What?

1478
01:36:13.938 --> 01:36:16.396
But I saw Trevor kill her.

1479
01:36:16.563 --> 01:36:19.146
Look. we don't know yet

1480
01:36:19.313 --> 01:36:21.146
but she's hanging on.

1481
01:36:24.063 --> 01:36:26.354
I... I wanna see her.

1482
01:36:26.521 --> 01:36:28.354
She's not awake yet.

1483
01:36:28.521 --> 01:36:31.771
And she may not remember anything.

1484
01:36:31.938 --> 01:36:34.271
You'll have to help her with that.

1485
01:36:34.438 --> 01:36:35.854
All in time.

1486
01:36:36.021 --> 01:36:37.854
Just get some rest now. OK?

1487
01:36:39.521 --> 01:36:41.229
Your attention. please.

1488
01:36:41.396 --> 01:36:44.771
There will be a mandatory meeting
for all non-emergency personnel

1489
01:36:44.938 --> 01:36:47.771
in the basement conference room
in five minutes.

1490
01:37:02.896 --> 01:37:06.771
...mandatory meeting for
all non-emergency personnel

1491
01:37:06.938 --> 01:37:10.354
in the basement conference room
in five minutes.

1492
01:37:26.313 --> 01:37:30.229
Is she gonna be OK?
Yeah.

1493
01:37:30.396 --> 01:37:33.854
She's a strong kid.
She's gonna have to be.

1494
01:37:36.188 --> 01:37:38.146
She asked if you were OK.

1495
01:37:38.313 --> 01:37:40.563
She thinks you guys
should write a book together.

1496
01:37:40.729 --> 01:37:42.688
with your matching wounds.

1497
01:37:42.854 --> 01:37:44.771
Why. she was stabbed
in the shoulder?

1498
01:37:48.729 --> 01:37:50.771
How did she know I was too?

1499
01:37:55.896 --> 01:37:57.729
Dammit!

1500
01:38:03.396 --> 01:38:07.063
You just won't die. will you?

1501
01:38:07.229 --> 01:38:10.271
Who are you. Michael fucking Myers?

1502
01:38:11.729 --> 01:38:13.396
Yeah. I don't think so.

1503
01:38:18.146 --> 01:38:20.104
Fucking die already!

1504
01:38:43.521 --> 01:38:45.104
How are those stitches?

1505
